OL,3,CBishop of Rochester says Church
OL,4,Csafeguarding needs 'change in culture'
OL,6,FThe Diocese of Rochester, the Church
OL,7,Fof England covering Medway, north and
OL,8,Fwest Kent, and the London Boroughs of
OL,9,FBromley and Bexley, has voted to pass
OL,10,Fa motion of No Confidence in the
OL,11,FArchbishops' Council's oversight of
OL,12,FSafeguarding.
OL,14,FThe Bishop of Rochester has led calls
OL,15,Ffor urgent reform to the Council,
OL,16,Fwhich is the senior governing body of
OL,17,Fthe Church of England.
