OL,3,CBishop of Rochester says Church
OL,4,Csafeguarding needs 'change in culture'
OL,6,FIt comes following the resignation of
OL,7,Fthe Archbishop of Canterbury, Justin
OL,8,FWelby, after he admitted failures of
OL,9,Fsafeguarding.
OL,11,FThe Rev Nathan Ward, Vicar of St
OL,12,FMargaret's who tabled the motion said:
OL,13,F"This decision reflects the Synod's
OL,14,Fgrave concerns regarding the findings
OL,15,Fof multiple independent reports
OL,16,Fhighlighting safeguarding failures and
OL,17,Fsystemic issues within the Church of
OL,18,FEngland.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
