OL,3,CBishop of Rochester says Church
OL,4,Csafeguarding needs 'change in culture'
OL,6,F"This motion is not a call for
OL,7,Fcondemnation but a humble
OL,8,Facknowledgment of the Church's shared
OL,9,Fresponsibility to protect the
OL,10,Fvulnerable and rebuild trust.
OL,12,F"We call upon the Archbishops' Council
OL,13,Fto undertake urgent and meaningful
OL,14,Freforms, as recommended by the
OL,15,Freports, to ensure accountability,
OL,16,Fprofessionalism, and transparency in
OL,17,Fsafeguarding.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
